@url=http://localhost:3000
@token=your_token_here

### Lista todos los conductores
GET {{url}}/conductores
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener un conductor por ID
GET {{url}}/conductores/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear un conductor
POST {{url}}/conductores
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nombre": "Carlos",
    "apellido": "García",
    "dni": "12345678",
    "licencia": "B12345",
    "fecha_vencimiento_licencia": "2026-12-31"
}

### Modificar un conductor
PUT {{url}}/conductores/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nombre": "Carlos",
    "apellido": "García",
    "dni": "12345678",
    "licencia": "B12345",
    "fecha_vencimiento_licencia": "2027-12-31"
}

### Eliminar un conductor
DELETE {{url}}/conductores/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



